Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.43,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}對白校對:{\fscx90}Isonkwan{\r} 灰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:40.43,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0300)}繁體校正:{\fscx90}simon_9331
