Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.87,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}現在的你 全力支持著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.62,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在的我 也有了支持你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.63,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使彷徨無助 我們也要結伴前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.75,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}奔向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.76,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然與朋友們嬉戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}這樣一路走來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻依然感到內心的空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.69,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受盡冷漠的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:51.86,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}寄身於時代的狂風中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:01:00.49,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}勇氣與不安 如影相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:08.38,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}因此 現在就要用我的雙手創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.55,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}那些讓我們受傷感到絕望的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.89,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些令我們哭泣感到難過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然縈繞於心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們終將跨過重重障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.11,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}以超越所有人為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.87,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}君が今僕を支えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.62,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕が今君を支える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.63,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから迷いながらも共に生きていこうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.75,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.76,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲間と戯れ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}それなりで居ても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もの足りなさを感じてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.69,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷めた目で見られて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:51.86,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}乾いた時代の風に吹かれている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:01:00.49,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}不安な心と勇気が背中合わせになっている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:08.38,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}だけど今なら夢をこの手で叶えてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.55,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}傷ついて壊れそうな日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.89,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙して困らせる日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕達はそれを越えていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.11,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}誰より上を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:46.35,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在哪裏呢？{\fad(300,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:50.18,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的寶藏{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:56.23,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在即將展開大冒險{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.86,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔和的陽光{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.90,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶給我啟程的預感{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:06.16,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 天空和花朵都在向我微笑{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:10.87,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前方等待我的將是什麼呢？{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.00,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:18.79,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕開啟夢想之門…{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:21.17,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「  走吧！」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:23.51,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使狂風吹襲{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:25.18,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使內心動搖{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:29.89,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使手中握著的是空白的地圖{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.68,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使狂風吹襲{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.56,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要描繪美好的明天{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:38.19,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著遠方  去往何方？ 直到那最終的彼方{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.15,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不言敗{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.94,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不哭泣{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:46.70,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到夢想成真的那一天{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.78,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空在微笑{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:50.45,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花兒也在微笑{\fad(100,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:54.33,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我也一定會開懷大笑{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:58.84,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何艱難險阻都能跨越{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:04.13,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也 再也…不會害怕了{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:46.35,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこにあるのかな{\fad(300,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:50.18,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ボクだけの宝物{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:56.23,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今 大きな冒険へ{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.86,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やわらかな日差し{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.90,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅立ちの予感{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:06.16,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空も花も ホラ 笑っている{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:10.87,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この先には何が待つのだろう？{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.00,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:18.79,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢の扉にそっと手をかけて…{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:21.17,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「  行こう！」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:23.51,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風に吹かれながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:25.18,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心揺らしながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:29.89,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真っ白な地図を片手に持ちながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.68,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風に吹かれながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.56,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日を描きながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:38.19,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠くまで 何処まで？ たどり着けるまで{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.15,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶対負けないよ{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.94,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶対泣かないよ{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:46.70,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この夢を叶えるその日までは{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.78,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの空は笑っていた{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:50.45,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの花は笑っていた{\fad(100,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:54.33,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ボクもいつか笑うから{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:58.84,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんな壁も越えるから{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:04.13,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう 何も 何も…コワクナイ{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【註釋】
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「寺子屋」慶典?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:04.27,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「寺子屋」：江戶時代的民眾教育機構 類似私塾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「塔矢名人選死活題集」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.89,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「死活題」：是指局部跟死活有關的棋型習題 日本稱為「詰棋」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將棋要比圍棋好玩100倍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:13.92,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「將棋」：日本將棋與中國象棋類似 均以將死對方為目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【對白】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安時代的棋師 藤原佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.43,0:00:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越了遙遠的時空 在進藤光的心中復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了領悟「神之一手」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:01:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}{\fnsimhei}{\bord2}{\i1}{\pos(405,370)}將棋社的加賀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道… 剛剛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不該把他強拉過來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他下得怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈局非常完美 一點破綻都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是職業棋手的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能說他的開局是無懈可擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於棋力方面就很難講了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的那一手十分精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很像是壞棋…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然控制了我的身體!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制我的心還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想對我身體下手嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能會那種拿子的姿勢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能會控制你的身體的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說是我自己下的嘍?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你用那邊的石頭試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指像這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不行嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是剛剛就是小光自己下的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且下的位置和我指示的也不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還想狡辯? 明明就是想控制我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不理你了 隨便你怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那的確是你自己下的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你學了一段時間的圍棋後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想自己下的意識變得強烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 塔矢名人拿子的姿勢真的好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢一直是在他的指導下學圍棋的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連棋子都拿不好 差得可太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次 用這塊石頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 小明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛我去小光家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候你去哪兒了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下圍棋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍棋? 又是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光最近好像很迷圍棋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰迷那東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35}{\fnsimhei}{\bord2}{\frz35}{\3c&H0F0F0F\1c&HC2BAEE&}{\pos(268,280)}章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}{\fnsimhei}{\bord1}{\frz42}{\c&H0F0F0F&}{\3c&HC2BAEE&}{\pos(160,394)}葉瀨中學校慶 ￥200
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐的學校有個校慶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來還想請你去吃章魚燒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星期天2點在葉瀨中學門口…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回去吃拉麵了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  2點在葉瀨中學門口見!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦 和女生去那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會被大家嘲笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子好像很喜歡小光哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 你又胡說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:52.38,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(110,165,110,-110)}{\fs20\fr270}{\fn@方正准圆_GBK}{\bord1}{\1c&H6972C5&}{\3c&HE2E7E0&}歡迎光臨葉瀨中學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:50.65,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(295,121,295,-30)}{\fs20}{\bord0}{\1c&H6E564A&}葉瀨中學校慶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有來嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是校慶嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就和那個差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我都沒帶錢來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 我買章魚燒回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃的樣子 我也想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏 有人在下圍棋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那邊吧 好嘛 好嘛 好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只看一小會兒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是中級難度的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請接下來走3步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先黑子「靠」 是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後白子… 下到這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走這裏呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 還真是很難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本書是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:08:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能答對死活題 這本書就作為獎品送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 我要 我要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讀幾年級?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學6年級
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們來點簡單點的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個的話我自己就可以應付了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為先不要講
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯…不錯… 答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 紙巾!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有更難一點的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更難一點的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 交給你嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是有段者的題目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個連我都覺得很難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先下3步看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就答出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 橙汁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要那本死活題集 給我一道最難的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最難的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個你也能做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和塔矢亮同一水平了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢亮?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的那麼厲害嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他應該可以通過職業考試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說他還和大人下指導棋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢亮或許可以解開這道題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一步是關鍵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢亮可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要自己試試看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一步…不就是這裏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍棋簡直無聊死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢亮算什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙不過是我的手下敗將而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢輸給你了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經是職業水平了 怎麼可能會輸給你?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比他強多了 白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫加賀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前和塔矢亮是一個圍棋學校的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這道死活題有點難度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他竟然一下子就知道答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人…是什麼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒井
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要成立的圍棋社怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連招收社員都很困難吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條件可以的話我也可以出賽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍棋社?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們學校沒有圍棋社的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能湊齊3個人去參加團體賽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校就同意我們成立圍棋社了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我的水平吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你要強1000倍以上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不需要\n那種把口香糖粘在棋盤上的人來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 說得倒好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道上次大賽是誰來求我去參賽的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著這個趕快消失!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「塔矢名人選死活題集」?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 對圍棋…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有塔矢亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最討厭了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你憑什麼恨塔矢亮嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「憑什麼」?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想教訓我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太自以為是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的膽子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪只手?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜對的話 我什麼都可以說給你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了的話 我可得把你揍得向我認錯為止!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要無理取鬧了 加賀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有覺悟的話就不要口出狂言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好不要理他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他好勝心很強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想決勝負的話就用圍棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我就贏給他看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不能保證一定會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的好勝心很強?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻手!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承認你夠膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棋子不見了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然上這種當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個沒大腦的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要再玩什麼無聊的圍棋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是跟我學下將棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以從頭好好教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我跟你學的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寧願一輩子不下將棋!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個不要吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你贏了塔矢!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一定是用了剛才那種卑鄙的手段吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就是塔矢根本沒盡全力!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定是下圍棋混不下去才去下將棋的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒井 放開他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都這麼說了 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就讓你見識見識我的實力!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我輸了的話 要我跪下都行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你輸了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就給我跳進游泳池裏去冬泳!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言為定!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17·四 右上角 「小目」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什麼拿子的姿勢啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用什麼姿勢關你什麼事!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15·四
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逞強的話等贏了我再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種小鬼怎麼可能明白我的感受?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵男
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鐵男
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一次也沒贏過那孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個塔矢亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有他在你總是第二名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明比他大了2歲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得丟臉嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然想贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 塔矢他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你一定要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則就不要回家了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強者始終是強者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的圍棋水平的確比其他人都要高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無疑問是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天本大爺肯定會贏你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後成為第一名的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…輸給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「輸給你吧」!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少看不起人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少看不起人了 少看不起人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把他當成是我的勁敵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他卻從來不把我放在眼裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我是輸是贏他都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終盤的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算上貼目我贏了1目半
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能嚥下這口氣!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有他在我就成不了第一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸知道後乾脆就把我放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個傢伙都是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 這小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子下得還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子竟然把我牽制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11·十五
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14·十六
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人雖然沒有塔矢亮那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還可以和我一步一步地周旋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然贏他沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還想和他多下一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然黑子看上去沒什麼優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過應該沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局勢不分上下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 黑子比較有利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.89,0:19:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9·十九
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}尤其是本橋 他臉都氣紅了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小明?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}還說「開什麼玩笑」…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙現在才來?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 該你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 不是那裏!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼等等?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12·十五
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的那一手可是致命的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒? 那麼多!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣? 要投降嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的游泳池在召喚你呢
